Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我進來咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把水端來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:06.00,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,370)}在繪馬上祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,38.5度  感冒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你要好好看好自己的身體才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸媽們今天也都去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫你去買點藥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了  你還得上學去不是嗎  惠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  把姐姐一個人丟下也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是小孩子了  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天你可要好好反省啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  請慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得惠似乎想拿全勤獎的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我可不是為了全勤才去的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先睡一覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來最近好像有說起過感冒正在流行的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天優子好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這肯定是遲到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  渚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有感冒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得小心點為好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大清早的到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這裏也來了一樣的短信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然間到底是哪根筋搭錯了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來短信了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:42.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}感冒了今天請假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:42.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}雖然有點發熱  不過你們不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:42.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}加油學習哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子好像感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:47.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神好像還不錯  但是熱度還不低
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡個一天大概就會治好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很不放心呢  要去探望下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我想見見她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就趕緊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太急了點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天據說優子請假了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說關於優子感冒請假…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天透透沒精神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗出得睡衣黏糊糊得好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:57.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}我現在跟倫還有透來看望你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:57.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:05:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家還真體貼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我不能穿成這樣來接待她們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕緊換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好久沒去優子家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿那麼正式你是想去哪裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然體溫還沒下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但僅僅有些困倦而已  沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  被傳染到感冒就不好了  我戴個口罩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  還得開窗通風
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外我再去泡杯茶去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我躺著去！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是今天的卷子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後這是慰問品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慰問品？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點痊癒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我們差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重身體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  優子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  優子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  還有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被傳染到了就不好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…今天家裏沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…感覺有點寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裏沒人的話就早說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃過東西了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直睡到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那過會兒我給你煮粥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿點給額頭降溫的東西來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之優子先躺下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先擦身再說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊  優子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現成的飯有  透
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要重新煮太費時間了  這可真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很熟練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家父母都是在工作的  這點小事早就已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到透你會這麼積極去照顧優子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過會兒去削蘋果  你先拿過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子肯定會很高興的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  透
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透你我為我做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃  真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  有點不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:09:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  不用那麼急…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等  怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那兩個人的關係果然很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要接嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推銷的話拒絕掉就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是優子家哦  說得像一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  我是優子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  推銷報紙的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  這個不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說要你用關西方言啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是削蘋果大會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  造型得是兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精細的活兒我做不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全削不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫  我們不能輸給…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小渚？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫的兔子好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅只隔了一間房  但是好像距離得好遠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想離得近一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子  做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隻身調任去東京嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:10:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會因為方言很奇怪而被捉弄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子你不會有問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣乘上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開車啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  雖然有點不安  但是加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京是什麼樣的地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子  外面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  好像看你有念叨著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  兩個人都睡著了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看護的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為交換啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能教我削蘋果的秘訣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,削皮？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是好晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你們睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東西買回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:32.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友來探望我的時候帶來了各種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你買的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是…  再說你肚子也飽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得惠替我買來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  叫透的孩子也來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還幫我煮了粥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透可是個能幹的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是問下來沒來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說惠子的姐姐好像跟模特兒一樣漂亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  在說我家小優嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體型是不錯啦  不過很普通吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:34.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼樣的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  家務萬般全能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別擅長做料理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天早上都幫我做便當的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習也不差  腦袋也不笨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之有點友善過度在些奇怪的地方讓人很糾結
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在男生裏應該很有人氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是引以為豪的姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼喋喋不休的惠子也好少見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？沒沒沒沒這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很正常的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能贏得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上下都被封住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…使不出力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  小倫…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不甘心  明明…不想輸給它的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  不可以在被爐裏睡覺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:30.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}被爐+電熱毯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是煮年糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下要去新年參拜  一定要起來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  透
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年參拜什麼的也不用晚上搞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種冷到死的天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的嘛  神社的新年參拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不出發就要趕不上電車了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  我計算好了  還有5分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許有近道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們慢悠悠地過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力衝刺到檢票口刷卡的話就來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太過分啦  渚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人果斷多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫她們到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道她在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我下來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:07.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}揮手揮得太HIGH了  忘記下車了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆瓜嗎  那傢伙是呆瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除夕敲鐘的隊伍排得好長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排第一的是從幾小時前開始排的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼冷的天還真是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除夕敲鐘是希望煩惱退散  迎來新的一年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過她也太拘泥於此了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰拘泥了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:42.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}排第一的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼頭老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始敲鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們最後敲好了  去看看其他東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買個護身符吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:58.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年還沒到呢  不賣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:16:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的時候買一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多種類啊  買哪個好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交通安全
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫一直很危險  買個替身護身符比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買哪個好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子就買那個好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避凶除災的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒那麼誇張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有那麼容易引災上身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到新年了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要在過年的時候第一個說「恭賀新年」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現甜酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在浪費我們時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預兆吉利呢  感覺一年都可以有好運
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭賀新年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二件事才是恭賀新年嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭賀新年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一搞慶賀就會很HIGH了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直很HIGH的好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭賀新年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭賀新年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有很多熟人來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  熟人都是誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來今天HIGH的程度又上了個檔次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來都是不認識的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望只能求一個的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這樣比較容易實現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求個什麼呢  那個嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  其他的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說馬上就要到我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…啊不這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我重新去排隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候你就會決定下來了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  香錢準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我準備好五日元了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了  優子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區五日元就想實現願望那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為五日元就可以打發神明了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒誠意  要有把錢包裏所有的錢都奉上的心情才對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞錯了把錢包丟進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說後天過來取
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能回來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真得注意點才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就是一年後了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有抽籤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去試試今年的運勢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽籤抽籤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢包找回來了要還我錢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備  開！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吉  居然是第二等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,末吉  好微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:19:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  是凶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種明顯輸掉的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簽是大吉  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運氣不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分我一點分我一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛主保佑  佛主保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我摸我摸我摸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家過來下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多繪馬哎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個  這個說她想開間花店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪馬真是個有趣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:46.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}希望今年一年透同學可以過得愉快健康——鬼頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的透是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏還有柚多谷的  莫非把班級裏所有人都寫了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定真做得出…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  我們也來寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那麼我們開始寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除夕敲鐘  人也退的差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.17,0:22:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.91,0:23:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.82,0:23:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那話是怎麼說得來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.92,0:23:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望煩惱退散  為迎來新的一年而敲的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.10,0:23:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩惱退散  原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.11,0:23:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚的煩惱快消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚的煩惱快消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.70,0:23:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下一個就是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.61,0:23:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子你不會這麼幹的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年也想來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.00,0:23:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.49,0:23:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次至少也要下午來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.68,0:23:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易一起出來了  就去我家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.67,0:23:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一起看第一次日出如何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.80,0:23:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊  贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.68,0:23:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是想去山上看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會那麼拼命的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.35,0:23:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.45,0:23:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  剛才的繪馬  大家寫了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.02,0:24:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寫了「希望家人們都可以幸福」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.76,0:24:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好普通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.20,0:24:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚無非就是那個吧  減肥什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.27,0:24:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.62,0:24:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透寫了什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.68,0:24:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半就是寫了「和倫可以更好的一起相處」是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用特意隱藏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.92,0:24:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.25,0:24:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.92,0:24:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透真是個害羞的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.17,0:24:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.38,0:24:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫肯定是「想吃很多甜點」  對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.82,0:24:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉你答錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.79,0:24:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  應該是前陣子想要的衣服吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.27,0:24:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個可以用壓歲錢來買
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.57,0:24:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快告訴我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.13,0:24:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個呢  大家一定都是一樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.90,0:24:51.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}希望四個人可以永遠好好相處下去  ——透
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.42,0:24:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  透？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.68,0:24:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.30,0:26:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見！
